   198	
   199	**Source:** KBM REQ-018 (`BRD_CRM_v1.0.md` §5); Pivot CRM BRD does not specifically address per-rep forecast accuracy
   200	
   201	**KBM's approach.** KBM specified forecast accuracy tracking by user over time — comparing forecasted vs. actual revenue per rep to identify accurate forecasters, learn from best practices, and coach developing forecasters. KBM's approach reflects their focus on data quality and continuous improvement of forecasting reliability.
