   209	## 3.04.5 Recommendation summary
   210	
   211	The merged-company Order Management playbook in shorthand:
   212	
   213	- **Transaction structure:** Separate linked transactions (Opportunity → Proposal/Quote → Sales Order → DPO/VPO/Invoice) with project number as primary reference and KBM's transaction-prefix scheme
