   121	**Recommendation for the merged company.** Migrate historical data sufficient to support merged-company historical reporting, period-over-period analysis, predictive analytics (per BI §3.09 D-7a), and audit-trail continuity. The specific cutover-back date is determined during data-migration planning with finance and BI leadership input — KBM's 2017 baseline and Pivot's D365 history both contribute.
