   925	| REQ-024 | Project GP vs. Commissionable GP tracking | Custom calculated fields + reporting | ACCOMMODATE | High | **Dependent on REQ-023** |
   926	| REQ-025 | Role-based permission visibility | Role/Permission setup with field-level visibility | ACCOMMODATE | Medium | **Dependent on REQ-023** |
   927	
   928	#### Implementation Approach - SESSION 3 REQUIRED
